content: /*<![CDATA[*/ $('#title').html($('meta[name=map-description]').attr('content')); /*]]>*/ Cloud Email and Collaboration Protection supports reporting emails to administrator-specified mailboxes March 22, 2024—Cloud Email and Collaboration Protection provides you the option to allow your end users to report emails through its add-in to mailboxes you have specified. Administrators can easily access the reported emails to analyze, investigate, and take necessary actions.
